+/**
+  * kbase_invoke_smc_fid - Perform a secure monitor call
+  * @fid: The SMC function to call, see SMC Calling convention.
+  * @arg0: First argument to the SMC.
+  * @arg1: Second argument to the SMC.
+  * @arg2: Third argument to the SMC.
